Package: restless
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: API topology inference CLI
 Restless discovers, models, inspects, and explains API surfaces from the
 terminal. It performs bounded, same-host API discovery using safe HTTP
 methods, infers endpoint structure, stores session state using XDG paths,
 and supports offline fixture-based inspection for reproducible tests.
